Project: Event Digest E-mailer
Author: Ryan Bubinski, ryanbubinski@gmail.com, 2010.
Purpose: Uses a Google Calendar and e-mail listserv to automagically generate 
         a periodic events digest e-mail

I. USE
1) Enter the proper configuration details in config.ini.php.
2) Set up a cron job to run email.php on a configured mail server.
3) Enjoy.

II. Libraries
PHPMailer v5.1 by codeworxtech (http://phpmailer.worxware.com/)
